        "heading": "Premium Chinese tea, curated with care",
        "text": "<p>Every tea in our collection is chosen for its character in the cup — the nutty sweetness of Longjing, the floral lift of a Fujian oolong, the depth of a well-aged pu-erh.</p><p>Our mission is to bring the best of Chinese loose-leaf tea to discerning drinkers who value quality, transparency, and the quiet pleasure of a well-made cup.</p>",
